  description="Expert Garland appliance repair for commercial ranges, ovens, griddles, grills, charbroilers, fryers, broilers, induction units, countertop equipment, and professional kitchen appliances. Professional Garland repair, maintenance, and installation support."
  ogImage="/garland/garland-appliance-repair-los-angeles-orange-county-ventura-county.webp"
